request.description:
# 💊 Pharmacy Services Catalog

Returns all **active** pharmacy services grouped by category. Call this once on app boot to build the service picker UI.

### Response shape
```json
{
  "data": [
    {
      "category": "clinical",
      "label": "Clinical",
      "services": [
        { "id": 4, "name": "Pharmacist Consultation", "slug": "pharmacist-consultation", "description": "...", "icon": "heroicon-o-chat-bubble-left-right" }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

### Categories
`dispensing` · `clinical` · `diagnostic` · `lab` · `delivery` · `wellness` · `specialized` · `operational`
